1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 36 MRSA ยง1760, sub-ยง116 is enacted to read:
3 116. Diapers. Beginning January 1, 2026, sales of disposable and reusable diapers,
4 including diaper covers, wraps and diaper fasteners that are used with reusable diapers. For
5 the purposes of this subsection, "diaper" means an absorbent garment worn by humans who
6 are incapable of or having difficulty controlling their bladders or bowel movements that is
7 marketed to be worn by adults or children.
8 SUMMARY
99 This bill provides a sales tax exemption for disposable and reusable diapers, including
1100 diaper covers, wraps and diaper fasteners, that are marketed to be worn by adults or
1111 children.
